{"tid":1449552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:25.000Z","uid":119804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0eeb914138731db242ea722dff65c1c772e41ff","tid":1449552,"uid":119804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=7d92d391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a6a93edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"6203d14c1031c82fd3f8dec3c9a0c973db917b8c","tid":1449552,"uid":276066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4d4628669ab1610aa043f59c7cbb75e1a9b7379","tid":1449552,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}